1. Define a helper method to perform the overlap calculation:

```csharp
public static IEnumerable<Range<long, long>> OverlapRanges(Range<long, long> range1, Range<long, long> range2)
{
    // Check if the ranges have no overlap
    if (range1.EndExcl <= range2.StartIncl || range2.EndExcl <= range1.StartIncl)
